f9dasm (1.83-1foundry2) resolute; urgency=medium

  * Add Foundry-Linux-authored man pages for f9dasm(1), hex2bin(1),
    mot2bin(1), and cmd2mot(1) — upstream ships none, and lintian's
    no-manual-page warning is a real Debian Policy §12.1 violation
    (every binary in /usr/bin/ must have a man page). With this revision
    lintian is clean of E: and W: lines.

